ferris-wheel-scatter-plot-w-curve.png.description: Graph of a periodic wave passing through the points from our ferris wheel dataset with local minima at about (0,5), (30,5), (60,5), (90,5) and local maxima at about (15, 205), (45, 205), (75,205), and (105,205)
ferris-wheel-scatter-plot-w-curve.png.source: Created by the Bootstrap team, with contrived data using Desmos

recent-co2-scatter.png.description: Scatter plot showing global CO2 levels over time, rising from December 2022 to May 2023, then dropping to December 2023. a few lighter dots are present from before December 2022 to hint at the nature of the curve.
recent-co2-scatter.png.source: Created by the Bootstrap team, with data from http://scrippsco2.ucsd.edu/data/atmospheric_co2
